PrecisAuthorization for the trip to NEW YORK CITY made by six Members of Parliament, from July 26 to July 28, 1995, in order to provide support to the efforts of the Department of Fisheries and Oceans to obtain a binding convention as an outcome of the sixth negotiating conference of the United Nations Conference on Straddling Fish Stocks and Highly Migratory Fish Stocks.
